name: Fish War: World of Shark - Hungry Feeding Game
name_original: Fish War: World of Shark - Hungry Feeding Game
description:
Welcome to Fish War,

You are a very aggressive fish, wandering around the ocean and eating smaller fishes to grow. Likewise, larger fishes out there seeking to eat you. Survive at long as you can, grow as big as you can and comparing your high score to other players around the world!
